PrecisEnactment of the WATERLOO-GUELPH AIRPORT ZONING REGULATIONS - which, for the purposes of aeronautical safety, place the usual restrictions on the height of new or existing structures and objects of natural growth, and prohibit using land lying within a four-kilometre radius of the airport located at Kitchener, Ontario, for the disposal of garbage that is edible by or attractive to birds.

precis:
Enactment of the WATERLOO-GUELPH AIRPORT ZONING REGULATIONS - which, for
the purposes of aeronautical safety, place the usual restrictions on the
height of new or existing structures and objects of natural growth, and
prohibit using land lying within a four-kilometre radius of the airport
located at Kitchener, Ontario, for the disposal of garbage that is edible
by or attractive to birds.
